URamaphosa kulindeleke ukuthi aphawule ngokudayiswa kotshwala nangezinkonzo zePhasika. Ihhovisi likamengameli limemezele ezinkundleni zokuxhumana ukuthi uRamaphosa uzokhuluma nabantu bakuleli ngezakamuva ezithinta iCovid-19. Emasontweni edlule abaholi bezenkolo bafakele uhulumeni ingcindezi yokuthi avume kwenyuswe isibalo sabazalwane ezinkonzweni ngempelasonto yePhasika.